  "title": "Principal Consultant/Associate Director",
  "description": "<p>We’re a forward-thinking recruitment firm that partners with high-growth companies to build exceptional teams. Our consultants are more than matchmakers—they’re strategic advisors, market analysts, and brand ambassadors. If you're early in your career and ready to build influence, this is where your journey begins.</p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Be part of the Pioneer batch of this start up and shape it for the future generations of recruiters.</li><li>Partner with clients to understand hiring needs, team culture, and business goals</li><li>Source and engage candidates through digital platforms, referrals, and events</li><li>Conduct structured interviews and assess candidate fit across multiple dimensions</li><li>Present candidate shortlists with clear rationale and market insights</li><li>Manage offer negotiations and onboarding coordination</li></ul><p>What You’ll Gain</p><ul><li>Happy working environment with great colleagues</li><li>Communication base salary + performance-based incentives</li><li>Hybrid work flexibility and modern office environment</li><li>Career progression mapped with clear milestones</li><li>Exposure to high-growth companies and decision-makers</li><li>A collaborative culture that values initiative, integrity, and innovation</li></ul><p>Interested applicants please call me @ +65 91130054 or email <a href=\"mailto:marco.chong@ev-search.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">marco.chong@ev-search.com</a></p><p>EV Search: 23S1748,</p><p>Marco Chong Wei Choon: R1215814</p>",
